      <h1 class="section-title" style="color: white;">
        Embrace The <span>3rs</span> for a Cleaner Planet
      </h1>
 
      <div class="row g-4">
 
        <!-- Reduce -->
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
          <div class="card card-3r shadow-lg">
            <img src="pbl_image/learn_reduce.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Reduce">
 
             <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="card-title">Reduce</h3>
 
              <p class="card-text">Reducing means using fewer materials and avoiding unnecessary waste in daily life. Simple actions such as limiting single-use plastics, buying only what is needed, and choosing reusable products can help reduce pollution and conserve natural resources.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
 
        <!-- Reuse -->
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
          <div class="card card-3r shadow-lg">
            <img src="pbl_image/learn_reuse.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Reuse">
 
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="card-title">Reuse</h3>
 
              <p class="card-text">Reusing means using items again instead of throwing them away after one use. Reusable bags, bottles, containers, and donated items help reduce waste while saving materials and energy needed to produce new products.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
 
        <!-- Recycle -->
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mx-md-auto">
          <div class="card card-3r shadow-lg">
            <img src="pbl_image/learn_recycle.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Recycle" >
 
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="card-title">Recycle</h3>
 
              <p class="card-text">Recycling is the process of collecting and turning waste materials such as paper, plastic, glass, and metal into new products. Recycling helps reduce landfill waste, conserve resources, save energy, and protect the environment.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
 
      </div>
